{"tid":2320101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[WFH一齊玩] Travian Kingdom Com1x3 12月15號香港時間晚上8點開ser!","createTime":"2020-12-10T13:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T14:17:02.000Z","uid":56281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2bce32071510cf2736a22594e6c9f2a43c1e29ba","tid":2320101,"uid":56281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"一眾連登仔請留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信有唔少人玩過戰略遊戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係有咩好玩過同一班人一齊玩實時戰略遊戲Travian kingdom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊有好多人會認真玩com3x3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 60+ !<br />\n以下係新ser 開既時間:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCOM 3x3<br />\n9月22 日 香港晚上8點<br />\n傳送門 : <a href=\"https://www.kingdoms.com/com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kingdoms.com%2Fcom%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=53b66fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kingdoms.com/com/</a><br />\nTG Group: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/M3RyeRz1QKWmD68FgHgNSQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FM3RyeRz1QKWmD68FgHgNSQ&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=aac5fdae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/M3RyeRz1QKWmD68FgHgNSQ</a><br />\n------------------------分割線-----------------------------------<br />\n引言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uX1tDOH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuX1tDOH.png&h=b8136cbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咩係Travian kingdom ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTravian Kingdom 係一種戰爭遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。遊戲目標係透過軍事手段/外交手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撃敗敵國，奪得他國財寶，並成為全ser最成功既王國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yzYr99f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyzYr99f.jpg&h=96401f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係三國分立, 藍色係連登仔, 其他2色係敵國<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXSwBAg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXSwBAg.png&h=1ac13ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個玩家一開始會有一條村莊，可以發展種田發展經濟(4種資源)﹑再用資源起兵打人/搶人/破壞人地條村莊(幾日概遊戲成果)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nnTPVj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nnTPVj.png&h=03305386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a2RUzCJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2RUzCJ.png&h=3954cbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. travian kingdom 同舊版有咩唔同呢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩家們可以組成唔同既王國。勝利條件: 主要搶地盤 財寶<br />\n-同Kingdom可以一齊搶treasure,一齊擴展領土,亦係新版travian既精彩地方!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nKingdom: kingdom由一位King,一(數)位duke,同埋領土內既governors組成, 只有King可決定入邊個外交關係<br />\n不過<br />\n連登仔....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKwA3xQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKwA3xQ.png&h=a7a523f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-開AC個陣會有 2個role 簡: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Governor 同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />King (但成個遊戲有3個role: governor,king 同duke)<br />\nGovernor: 打robber hideout ,robber hideout 有資源+stolen good 攞，stolen good 賣左有資源(最多係crop) 一日(24hrs)可能有2-3個到，冇點計過<br />\nKing: 冇robber hideouts 但可以有收tribute(最少係crop)<br />\nDuke有robber hideout 同tributes 收, 但hideout數量會少一半，tribute 多唔多睇你3x3 4x4 多唔多人咁<br />\n**duke係king委任的，重課同長on 優先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Secret Societies : 呢種盟係一個秘密租織,無要求你既村莊位置,任何玩家都可以加入,所有連登仔都會先入呢個SS同其他巴打取得聯繫先. 同SS可共享戰報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />secret society 主要係for 我地連登仔用中文交流(英文都OK) + 睇大家既troop 同crop production<br />\n大家記著要入埋secret society <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搬村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊版你一開始個account係邊個方位係冇得變。你想自已條村同朋友相鄰既話要開2村。<br />\n但係Travian kingdom 你開始個條村係可以搬位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以由(10|10)搬去(29|-31) , 咩方位都得! 所以如果你一開始條村符近好似有好多狼，你就搬就可以。 不過搬村係要搬係一個王國(後邊詳述)領土入邊，之前要有先由國王批准。<br />\n<br />\n我地會係開ser 一日內搬曬咁多位巴打去一個位，到時係tg group等消息就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打係空窗期可以試下起下田，冒下險咁(起到普5就好)<br />\n仲有單兵撞綠洲清棒棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />節奏快<br />\n起個件野如果 有5分鐘就起完既話， 可以免金 instant build<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 所以一開始跟住任務做就會可以係20分鐘內 資源田 全3 。<br />\n資源量﹑起野時間都比舊版travian 多。<br />\n出兵時間﹑起士兵(資源)都比舊版travian 少。<br />\n如果你係狼完全可以係2日內 出保開搶，再snowball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />壓力比舊版travian 細<br />\n如果王國領土入邊有攻擊既話，全個王國成員都會有紅箭咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。會知道被攻擊目標同到達時間。 好既王國會幫防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似下圖咁，紅色箭咀代表有玩家條村比人打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係只要係國土入邊就全員都會有警報睇，同埋有到達時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uWA3fk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uWA3fk.jpg&h=27aa37af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且禁入去條村可睇到有幾多防，同米(唔夠就有人會幫send)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaE69US.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaE69US.png&h=a0eaeb49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要一個連登仔有難，四面八方一定會有人支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為 搞連登仔死撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n***以往經驗係夠時間到就一會救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 救唔到(棒棒的話)都一定有人會追秒等清曬人地D棒棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />資源累積速度快<br />\ntravian kingdom 入邊個kingdom replace 左舊版 公會，個D 變左做王國<br />\n主要搶地盤 財寶。財寶多，成個王國既人賣stolen good 既資源就會越多!<br />\n新玩法<br />\nRelocation: 如果你冇入王國，而你又唔係你想入既王國既國界入邊，咁經書信同意既話國王會邀你去relocate 佢國界入邊。但relocate之後你所 有資源田LV 全變0。不過你所用到係資源田既資源全部會係你英雄個inventory 入邊，你想要幾多禁一個制就比番你。<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新既通訊介面<br />\n直接比圖!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rk4u7Gy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRk4u7Gy.png&h=1ce558f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbb2787e1f0970bc486fdb5b058645c0ce21dd1b","tid":2320101,"uid":56281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"引用舊Post新手Q&amp;A:<br />\n1. 點先開到2村?<br />\n滿意3個條件:<br />\n-2000 Culture Point (Town hall開一次party就有任送夠)<br />\n-10級 Residence (唔好起錯Palace)<br />\n-3隻Settler<br />\n<br />\n2.我玩既時間唔多, 又唔想做羊, 點好?<br />\n做Governor,建議你防兵同人口至少有1:1比例,令敵人搶你都冇著數就自己唔會郁你, 同埋2村開過黎入聯盟生防兵(聯防係呢隻game既靈魂)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.我玩既時間好多, 又可以點做?<br />\n實力有返咁上下既巴打們,可以做我地king既duke, 唔需要交稅, 但要為佔地盤而開村<br />\n<br />\n4.咩係15田,9田?<br />\n因為每隻兵都會食糧, 主村開15田/9田可以養好多兵, 攻兵村專用<br />\n<br />\n5.好驚出保護期<br />\n冇野好驚, 你正常keep住有兵有資源田冇人會郁到你<br />\n<br />\n6.唔課金會唔會冇得打?<br />\n唔會, 當時課左會有著數啦, 我都建議少貨買個starter pack, 但隻GAME好睇合作, 齊心就唔怕課金王<br />\n課金就要買土耳其，便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普通既話課一隻火雞就夠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nW6QR8j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnW6QR8j.png&h=309b4e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n課左就係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cSax5R7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSax5R7.jpg&h=bb22acac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.我要出街/去旅行幾日冇得上網,點好?<br />\n可以係<a href=\"http://lobby.travian.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flobby.travian.com%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=313c0fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lobby.travian.com/</a> set其他玩家做你sitter(代管)或者duals(一齊共玩acc)咁就唔怕啦,我相信短時間既話好多巴打都可以幫<br />\n<br />\n8.電話版好唔掂喎,點搞?<br />\n官方個APP已經出左<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.traviangames.traviankingdoms&amp;hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.traviangames.traviankingdoms%26hl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=c304d3e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.traviangames.traviankingdoms&amp;hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n又或者用teamviewer遙控自己屋企部電腦玩啦<br />\n<br />\n9.好多時唔知起乜好?<br />\n跟任做基本就都保到你去2村架喇, 玩到2村都唔知做乜? 開3村囉<br />\n<br />\n10.我仲係好怕畀人打,點好?<br />\n出偵兵,你有偵兵係條村,人地要數量多過你既偵兵先偵到,通常偵唔到都唔會亂咁出兵打你<br />\n仲可以提下新手搶人之前要偵下人, 因為呢一版TR 基本一出世個個都有兵, 小心為上. 如果人地有英雄係屋企就要睇下人地英雄裝備, 有雞鞋會自動走兵.<br />\n<br />\n11. 幾多兵打人先得過?<br />\n遊戲入既Rally Point 有 Combat simulator, 衡量過先出兵, 免得死傷慘重, 然後比人羊化<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n巴打們想唔想征戰四方?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快D 入一齊玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住入黎L個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同 吹個靚水先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內有更詳細攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你鍾意:<br />\n撩交打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n種田食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嘴炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就一定唔好錯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5XpcDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5XpcDU.jpg&h=24d4f3d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L73Dg5B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL73Dg5B.png&h=0066e0f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DpAbDXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpAbDXG.jpg&h=69a2eb90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"279c03d9ec02f04e0e9b75db7ff65e27d6d350f1","tid":2320101,"uid":56281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"無敵既連登仔己經3連勝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打快d加入一齊玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貼多次tg link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/M3RyeRz1QKWmD68FgHgNSQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FM3RyeRz1QKWmD68FgHgNSQ&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=aac5fdae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/M3RyeRz1QKWmD68FgHgNSQ</a>"},{"pid":"5ce28ad58d626bc93e0cd65b5dc6975ffa3c900c","tid":2320101,"uid":43013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img